"Syntaxing
syntax on 

"Line numbers
set number 

"Wraps long lines in vim
set wrap 

"Sets left/right arrow keys and h/l to wrap to prev/next line
set whichwrap+=<,>,h,l 

"Applies indentation of current line to next
set autoindent 

"Reacts to current syntax/style of code
set smartindent 

"How long each tapstop will be
set tabstop=4 

"Shifted by 4 spaces
set shiftwidth=4 

"Will type spaces
set expandtab 

"Inserts blanks according to shiftwidth
set smarttab